  "title": "Investment Banking Analyst/Associate",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role Description</strong></p><p>This is a \nfull-time position located on site in Singapore for an Investment \nBanking Analyst/Associate covering Asia. They will be responsible for \nday-to-day tasks, including conducting research, preparing financial \nmodels, preparing marketing materials, and executing transactions. They \nwill work closely with other team members on data and financial \nanalyses, due diligence activities, and the creation of transaction \nmaterials. Being exposed to every aspect of a deal/transaction cycle, \nthe candidate will be involved in the deal sourcing process, evaluation \nof such opportunities, arranging and structuring of such transactions, \nand see to the completion and documentation. The role needs a go-getter \nwho wants to gain investment banking skills to eventually become a deal \nmaker.<br /></p><p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor's degree in Accountancy, Finance, Economics, or related field.</li><li>Candidates with experience in financial modeling, valuation, financial analysis and financial accounting.</li><li>Strong analytical skills, critical thinking, and attention to detail</li><li>Excellent\n communication and interpersonal skills, including the ability to work \ncollaboratively with cross-functional and international teams</li><li>Fresh Graduates are welcome to apply</li></ul>",
